<br>
IF ALL ELSE FAILS and they are not interested in doing a raid...then make the droppable loot /random for all(including the cof). It sucks....but it better to have a 1 in 40 shot at a cof than the raid not even starting. People will bitch and complain about CoF being randomed to all (ie all the mellers), but if this is a pickup raid, we all know the only worthwhile loot on naggy is his cof...the rest is...well...junk.<br>
<br>
Host enough of these and you WILL get your cof. AND if you find that you are 52 almost 53 and still no CoF. Then it is maybe a good idea to turn on AAXP 100%...get your run3 and regen 3 (for a few more weeks) just to keep at 52. Once you pass 52 there is a vaccum of good haste until you are in a solid guild doing dragon mobs.<br>
<br>
btw....forgot to mention...IF you had higher lvl friends...it would ROCK if you could get a cleric with Mass Group Buff Aego (I am sure you will find a cleric who would be interested in join a naggy raid for a shot at a cof). Also if you can score a high lvl shammy then your tanks will be ver nicely buffed with +2k hps approx.<br>
<br>
<br>
Good luck with your adventures <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
Cuch.<br>
